<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id795a7a00-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s1684"><num value="1684">§ 1684.</num><heading> Annual reports</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall make annual reports to the Congress on the programs authorized by this subchapter. These reports shall be submitted with the reports required under <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s1606/c">section 1606(c) of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id795a7a01-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/96/554/s5">Pub. L. 96–554, § 5</ref>, <date date="1980-12-19">Dec. 19, 1980</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/94/3258">94 Stat. 3258</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id795a7a02-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="id795a7a03-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="id795a7a04-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1981-10-01">Oct. 1, 1981</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/96/554/s9">section 9 of Pub. L. 96–554</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s1681">section 1681 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
